# Routing Guide

## Directory Structure
- app/
  - (auth)/ - Authenticated routes group
  - (public)/ - Public routes group
  - api/ - API routes
- components/
  - ui/ - Base components
  - features/ - Feature-specific components
- lib/ - Utilities and configurations

## Conventions
- Use layout.tsx for shared layouts
- Implement loading.tsx for Suspense
- Define error.tsx for error handling
- Keep page.tsx as single page file

## Middleware
- Authentication
- Redirects
- Security headers
- Rate limiting

